data.description: Wonderful property! Tremendous value! Beautifully remodeled house on large one third acre lot zoned RES-B with multiple options for dividing and building. Property includes 2 outbuildings: (25'x32') shop has three 220 outlets, garage door access - perfect for significant projects; and a finished shed (6'x8') with built-in shelving for additional interests. Buyer due diligence to confirm property details.The generous lot also has gardens, raised beds, and mature trees. The house has been transformed with slate tile floor, custom cabinets, refinished oak floors, and updated bathroom. Spacious primary bedroom could easily serve as a family room or large home office. Great location and open concept design - you will love living here!
